{"name":"Alchemy","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-content/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 29\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>To practice the sorcery-science of alchemy. Apprentice pyromancers learn how to identify potions by taste alone; albeit the practice is not always safe. At 7th level, a pyromancer may concoct potions with the assistance of an alchemist. By 11th level, the assistance of an alchemist is no longer required. For more information, refer to <strong>Chapter 7: Sorcery</strong>, <em>alchemy</em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"pyromancer","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.iPWkkv7WnyUR7Nbk"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679250807770,"modifiedTime":1681579252526,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"V9prO2MUZJewJtuH","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
{"name":"Scroll Writing","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-content/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 30\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>To scribe a known spell onto a scroll, creating a single-use magical device at a cost of 500 gp + 100 gp per spell level. Materials may include the finest vellum, paper, or papyrus; a fresh quill; and sorcerer&rsquo;s ink, such as sepia. This involved process requires one week per spell level.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"pyromancer","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.4qdWAUdJZir7pEeN"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679251303706,"modifiedTime":1681579252526,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"Y745EfC80l3UyEPY","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
